name: FEED HUNTER: GROW FISH BATTLE
description:
There is a fascinating wildlife in the deep underwater waiting for you! Use the diving suit and dive into the depths, enjoy the wonderful experience! There are also dangerous fish in the water, protect yourself from the predators with your speargun. Try to shoot as many as you can and collect as many points as you can!


Features:
-realistic swimming system
-several types of fish
-underwater impressive environment
